d Vitale, Vincenzo and Vodeb, Veronika and Voisin, Vincent and Vorobiov, Serguei and Voutsinas, Georgios Gerasimos and Vovk, Ievgen and Waegebaert, Vincent and Wagner, Stefan Joachim and Walter, Roland and Ward, Martin and Wechakama, Maneenate and White, Richard and Wierzcholska, Alicja and Will, Martin and Williams, David A. and Wohlleben, Frederik and Wolter, Anna and Yamamoto, Tokonatsu and Yamazaki, Ryo and Yang, Lili and Yoshida, Tatsuo and Yoshikoshi, Takanori and Zacharias, Michael and Sanchez, Ricardo Zanmar and Zavrtanik, Danilo and Zavrtanik, Marko and Zdziarski, Andrzej A. and Zech, Andreas and Zhdanov, Valery I. and Zi\c etara, Krzysztof and \v Zivec, Miha and Zuriaga-Puig, Jaume},
  date = {2023-10-11},
  eprint = {2310.07413},
  eprinttype = {arXiv},
