ue and family=Veggel, given=M, prefix=van, useprefix=true and family=Broeck, given=C, prefix=van den, useprefix=true and Vecchio, A and Veitch, J and Vetrano, F and Vicere, A and Vyatchanin, S and Willke, B and Woan, G and Yamamoto, K},
